        <mxCell id="120" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Flow Legend:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0000CC&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;① POST /api/admin/auth/login&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; - Admin/Teacher login → verify password → sign JWT → set httpOnly cookie&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0000CC&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;② POST /api/admin/auth/logout&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; - Logout → add token to blacklist&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0000CC&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;③ PUT /api/admin/auth/change-password&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; - Verify old password → update new password&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0000CC&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;④ GET /me + PUT /profile&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; - View/update admin profile (email, display name)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#009900&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;⑤ POST /api/agents/register&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; - Agent sends API Key → validate → upsert agent → sign JWT tokens (access + refresh)&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#009900&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;⑥ POST /api/auth/refresh&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; - Validate refresh token → issue new access token&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CC0000&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;⑦ RBAC Middleware&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; - Applied on ALL endpoints: require_role, require_admin, require_permission, inject_current_user&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Teachers: filtered data (only their groups/agents). Admins: full access.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Additional endpoints:&lt;/b&gt; POST /api/auth/verify, GET /api/auth/token-info, POST /api/auth/logout (agent), POST /api/admin/auth/refresh&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;resizable=1;points=[];autosize=0;strokeColor=#666666;fillColor=#f5f5f5;rounded=1;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="650" width="1000" height="280" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
