        <mxCell id="220" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Flow Legend:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0000CC&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;① POST /api/agents/heartbeat&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; - Agent sends CPU/RAM/disk metrics every 20s → update status → SocketIO broadcast (agent_heartbeat)&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Server response may include force_sync flag → trigger whitelist re-sync&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0000CC&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;② POST /api/logs&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; - Agent sends batch of logs (domain access, firewall events) → bulk insert to MongoDB&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0000CC&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;③ GET /api/whitelist/agent-sync&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; - Agent requests whitelist (domains, patterns, IPs) with version check → incremental/full sync&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#009900&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;④ CRUD /api/agents/*&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; - Admin: list, view, delete, update display-name, update position, assign group (13 endpoints)&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#009900&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;⑤ PATCH /api/agents/&amp;lt;id&amp;gt;/policy&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; - Set agent policy: whitelist_only, monitor, custom rules → SocketIO broadcast (agent_policy_changed)&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#009900&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;⑥ GET /api/logs + /stats&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; - View logs with filters (level, agent_id, time_range) + statistics + export + clear&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;SocketIO events:&lt;/b&gt; agent_registered, agent_heartbeat, agent_deleted, agent_group_updated, agent_policy_changed, new_log, logs_cleared&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;resizable=1;points=[];autosize=0;strokeColor=#666666;fillColor=#f5f5f5;rounded=1;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1">
